messages.content: The next election is a straight choice between a Labour Government fighting for you, your family and the NHS or five more years of the Conservatives putting the most privileged first. Vote Labour and make your vote count.
"If you choose me as your MP, I will be a champion for equality, decent jobs and sustainable economic growth."

leaflet.personalStatement: "If you choose me as your MP, I will be a champion for equality, decent jobs and sustainable economic growth."
